            "extractedText": "ONGLISH\tXI-English (MCQs), Page# 89\t\r\nPh\t\r\nOLON\tUnit# 01\tDEMOCRATIC CITIZENSHIP\t\r\nNote: Read the statements and encircle the right option.\t* national level\tThe Quaid-e-Azam was speaking to the Constituent Assembly at\tQuaid on 11\" August, 1947\t\r\n* make country as example\tThe main function of the Constituent Assembly was to__.\t* regional level * global level\t*provincial level\t\r\n* make constitution\t* honour assembly members\t\r\n3.\t* discrimination\tAccording to the Quaid-e-Azam, 'Cyclonic revolution\" meant a wave of\t* practice constitution\t\r\n* revolt\t\r\n4.\tThe main task of the Govt., according to the Quaid-e-Azam is to\t* elections\t* legislation\t\r\n* make constitution for provinces\t\r\n* curb bribery\t* stop black marketing\t\r\n5.\tAccording to the Quaid-e-Azam, the poisonous thing is\t* make law and order\t\r\n* corruption\t\r\n* nepotism\t* black-marketing\t\r\n6.\tThe colossal crime monster as stated in the text is\t*law and order situation\t\r\n* the law\t* black marketing\t\r\n* favoritism\t* bribery\t\r\n1. On 11\" August 1947, Quaid-e Azam was speaking to the\t* already functioning assembly\t\r\n* whole nation\t* first legislative body\t\r\n* members of the provincial body.\t\r\nThe first legislative body was bestowed with\t\r\n* with full powers\t* with limited powers\t\r\n* to only make legislative powers\t* with only powers to curb bribery\t\r\nThe thing that was already prevailing in the sub-continent after partition was\t\r\n* bribery\t* foodstuff\t* nepotism\t* starvation\t\r\n10. The guided principles of the Quaid-e-Azam Muhammad Ali Jinnah are\t\r\n* support & cooperation\t* justice & fair play\t\r\n* prejudice & honour\t* angularity of majority & minority\t\r\n",
